  "title": "Product Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Own product roadmap planning, ensuring alignment with business objectives and long-term vision.</li></ul><ul><li>Drive stakeholder engagement, balancing priorities across business, engineering, and design teams.</li></ul><ul><li>Oversee integration of new features and systems, ensuring seamless delivery and adoption.</li></ul><ul><li>Conduct market research and competitive analysis to inform product strategy.</li></ul><ul><li>Define clear product requirements and success metrics, ensuring measurable impact.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proven experience in product management, ideally within technology or data-driven industries.</li></ul><ul><li>Strong ability to translate business needs into actionable product strategies.</li></ul><ul><li>Excellent communication and stakeholder management skills.</li></ul><ul><li>Experience with agile methodologies and cross-functional collaboration.</li></ul><ul><li>Analytical mindset with a focus on outcomes and continuous improvement.</li></ul>",
