    "description": "<p>Mars Consulting is a rapidly growing provider of Human Capital Solutions &amp; Business Consulting Solutions, offering a wide range of mid to senior resources across multiple functions. We focus on providing resources &amp; headhunting services across specific areas such as Top Management, Enterprise Applications, IT, Sales &amp; Marketing, Finance &amp; Accounting, &amp; Human Resources. Our customers come from verticals including Banking &amp; Finance, IT, Service, Real Estate, Energy, &amp; Healthcare. As a highly customer-focused organization with expertise in managed services, our team consistently delivers exceptional solutions that meet and exceed our clients' expectations.</p>",
